story.text: Tom is back after us not seeing eachother for three weeks. He is a good boss - happy to be back in the passenger seat with him mostly at the wheel.
Still have a sore throat - not sure what it up. Hope it is gone shortly. It's Friday!!!!! YAYAYAYA.
Really in love with Montana and so damn happy to be here - I am one lucky man.
